.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There are 5 different favourite colors: aquamarine, purple, azure, chestnut, lavender
There are 5 different nationalities: indian, american, italian, spanish, australian
There are 5 different favourite beverages: 7up, almond-mirinda, mirinda, iced-tea, soy-milk
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: aquamarinemaster, siglo, vegafina, baccarat, old-henry
5 different pets are kept: rabbit, chinchilla, mouse, hamster, ferret
1. the indian is the person who likes azure
2. the swedish is the owner of the mouse
3. the american is the person drinking iced-tea
4. the person who likes purple is on the left of the person who likes chestnut
5. the person who likes purple is the person drinking almond-mirinda
6. the vegafina-smoker is the owner of the chinchilla
7. the person who likes lavender is the siglo-smoker
8. the person drinking mirinda is in the middle
9. the spanish is on the far left
10. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the owner of the rabbit
11. the owner of the ferrets is on the left or right of the siglo-smoker
12. the aquamarinemaster-smoker is the person drinking 7up
13. the italian is the baccarat-smoker
14. the spanish is on the left or right of the person who likes aquamarine
15. the old-henry-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking soy-milk

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Color		|    lavender	|     aquamarine	|      azure	|     purple	|     chestnut	|
| Nationality	|   spanish	|    american	|    indian	|    italian	|    swedish	|
| Pet		|     rabbit	|    ferret	|     chinchilla	|     hamster	|      mouse	|
| Beverage	|    soy-milk	|     iced-tea	|     mirinda	|    almond-mirinda	|      7up	|
| Cigar		|   siglo	|    old-henry	|  vegafina	|    baccarat	|   aquamarinemaster	|
